2026-04-12: <200ms p95 latency via RCS, N+1 elimination, CF
  - RCS: 5-min TTL user data, 15-min TTL project metadata; immediate invalidation on write
  - N+1 prevention via eager loading (JOINs) enforced by EXPLAIN ANALYZE on PRs; query complexity threshold enforcement
  - CF: S3 origin for static assets (versioned with content hash), ECS LB for dynamic; index.html no-cache, assets max-age=31536000
  - Page load targets: TTFB <100ms, FCP <1.5s, LCP <2.5s, CLS <0.1 via critical CSS, lazy-loaded images, font-display=swap
  - RUM and synthetic k6 monitoring; budget alerts fail deployment if bundle > 15% increase
  - Database pooling (min 5, max 20); microservice timeouts (2s to auth-service) prevent cascading failures
